00:19:37,593 --> 00:19:40,176
the Black Mercy granted you.

283
00:19:40,388 --> 00:19:42,720
Rrarr!

284
00:19:45,518 --> 00:19:46,679
Rraah!

285
00:19:48,604 --> 00:19:49,719
[crashing]

286
00:19:53,693 --> 00:19:54,808
Happy?

287
00:20:00,950 --> 00:20:03,567
Do you know what I've lost?

288
00:20:03,786 --> 00:20:06,323
thud thud

289
00:20:06,539 --> 00:20:09,201
What I've..

290
00:20:19,969 --> 00:20:22,006
You know, for a moment there

291
00:20:22,221 --> 00:20:24,303
(Mongul) 'I almost believed you were gonna kill me.'

292
00:20:24,515 --> 00:20:27,883
How stupid of you to hesitate like that.

293
00:20:28,102 --> 00:20:31,686
Not a mistake I'll make, I can assure you.

294
00:20:31,897 --> 00:20:34,229
