296
00:20:49,457 --> 00:20:52,666
This...this was your birthday present.

297
00:20:52,877 --> 00:20:54,333
A new breed of rose.

298
00:20:54,545 --> 00:20:56,877
Called the Krypton, but..

299
00:20:57,882 --> 00:21:00,465
Don't worry about it.

300
00:21:07,641 --> 00:21:09,348
I promise you.

301
00:21:09,560 --> 00:21:11,892
I'll never forget.

302
00:21:13,564 --> 00:21:14,599
I wonder what he's seeing.

303
00:21:17,943 --> 00:21:21,402
Whatever it is, it's too good for him.

304
00:21:24,492 --> 00:21:27,780
[people screaming]

305
